Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:26.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a \Npirate alliance with Trafalgar Law{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and have come to Dressrosa governed by \Nthe Warlord - Donquixote Doflamingo.{\i0}
