Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And finally, Luffy brought down Doflamingo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'd lost your memory \Nuntil two years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was that serious,\Nhow did you get your memory back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I think now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FIRE FIST ACE DIES
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The timing couldn't be any \Nworse than that but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that was why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he awakened my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Brothers' Bond!\NThe Untold Story Behind Luffy and Sabo's Reunion!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:43.95,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,TWO YEARS AGO - SABO (20 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sabo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sabo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just looking out at the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back in Baltigo\Nfor the first time in a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope everybody's doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we've been tied up with missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make a report to Dragon-{\i1}san{\i0} first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:52.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,BALTIGO\NTHE REVOLUTIONARY ARMY'S GENERAL HEADQUARTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hectic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Chief of Staff! You \Ncame at the right time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the situation room now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Paramount War between the Navy\Nand the Whitebeard Pirates has ended!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard lost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, one of the Four Emperors has\Nbeen taken down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy has a lot of casualties, too.\NSeems like it was a hard battle as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Ivan-{\i1}san{\i0}?! Is she alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't say she died or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who died in the war were...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Emperor - Whitebeard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Fire Fist Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly, Dragon-{\i1}san{\i0}, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true?!\NIs Straw Hat Luffy your son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FIRE FIST ACE DIES
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become a pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and defeat others and become infamous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be the only proof of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if all the people in the world\Nreject me or despise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become a great pirate\Nand show them what I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo-{\i1}kun{\i0}, what's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that Ace \Nwas Gold Roger's son...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the biggest threat to the Navy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they wanted to get rid of him at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you guys know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say Akainu punched a hole right\Nthrough his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can become brothers\Nif we exchange this cup of {\i1}sake{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brothers? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we become pirates,\Nwe might not be on the same ship
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but our brotherhood will always be with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever you are, whatever you do,\Nwe'll always be bonded together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.39,0:09:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Sabo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sabo-{\i1}kun{\i0}!\N--Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I know!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The one who died wasn't \Nsome unknown pirate...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He wasn't just some threat in the Pirate Era\Nthat needed to be eliminated!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ace is my...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...brother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna run from anybody!\NI'm not gonna lose to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The chief woke up!\N--Really?! That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were gonna die! Sabo-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had quite a high fever, Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been sleeping for three straight days!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've been worrying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You got your memory back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I remember everything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Including who I am and\Nwhy I left home and sailed out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna quit\Nthe Revolutionary Army, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is Dragon-{\i1}san{\i0} still here?\N--He is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, I felt Ace said to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You're Sabo.\NYou're Luffy's and my brother."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?! Don't interrupt now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you finish the bottle?! It's empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you eat all the meat as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't listen to such a \Nstory without drinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa-whoa, both of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we don't need alcohol
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we'll be in trouble without food\Nwhen Luffy wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of our crew eat so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go and get groceries \Nlater with Kin'emon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get some booze, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's friends are funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never get bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I wanna hear the rest already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally... managed to get here... Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this. Luffy started to make his way\Nto become the King of the Pirates again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our younger brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:28.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE STRAW HATS ARE BACK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sabo-kun?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to ask the entire \NRevolutionary Army a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a Devil Fruit that \NI want to get at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0},\Nwhat about the Flare-Flare Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.49,0:15:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna keep it out of \Nthe hands of a few people
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't have a choice! \NMy friend's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you I will win the Flare-Flare Fruit\Nso you can go out without worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! I appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you have the Flare-Flare Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Straw Hat Luffy"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey! Where you from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't talk to Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0} so casually!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the legendary pirate\N"Fire Fist" Ace-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s brother
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he will become the King of \Nthe Pirates one day, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've known that from way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just appear out of nowhere\Nand say you won't let me have the fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "It's me"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! The Flare-Flare Fruit \Nis a keepsake from Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, you're my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you called me "Luffy" but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...look at this beard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I can't tell my brother's face\Njust because he's in disguise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Brother"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, the only people who \Ncan call me their brother
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are the late Ace and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the guy who died much earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Died...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We stole a bottle of {\i1}sake{\i0} from Dadan\Nand made a toast...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...\NWhere have you been all this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sabo, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I let Ace get killed in front of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Even though Ace died, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so happy that you survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost helplessly lost both of my brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had also died,\NI would've been left on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for being alive, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I eat the Flare-Flare Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be nice!\NThat's the only option we've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... He's laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.42,0:19:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of a dream he's having.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm leaving now.\N--Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got to see his face so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I made a Vivre Card \Nof Luffy's just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, when did you have time for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a piece of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Luffy might be a \Nbit much for you to handle,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but take good care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You can count on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural for a big brother to worry\Nabout his bungling kid brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be a bit much for you to handle,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but take good care of 'im.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said the same thing Ace said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this Sabo? This is Hack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I just left the \Nhouse. I'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how was it? Luffy-{\i1}kun{\i0} was quite...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.99,0:20:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he hang up?! That selfish jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa-whoa! Hack-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.84,0:20:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Could you look at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's "one"...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... The only side that \Nwould be in Straw Hat's favor -
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's what we agreed on, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.10,0:21:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, he won this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't arrest him tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't determine that \Nwith a die roll! Issho-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ran across the entire country\Nand finally found where he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.86,0:21:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lashed out against\NFleet Admiral Sakazuki like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna take down Law and \NStraw Hat, now's the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maynard-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man shouldn't grumble like that\Nafter a die has been cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:42.99,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE ROYAL PALACE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anybody see Lucy after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, nobody did.\N--I wanna say "Thank you" to him at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's already quite a fuss out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they truly are pirates or criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.34,0:21:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're our saviors without question.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.73,0:22:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.33,0:22:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}, Lucy,\Nand the others aren't here at the Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah but don't worry. I \Ngot a call from Kyros.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.78,0:22:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.90,0:22:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I go back to being a king again,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.49,0:22:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be a princess, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.42,0:22:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we depart anytime?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:22:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Once we go back to Baltigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta tell Dragon-{\i1}san{\i0} so much about Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.17,0:23:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.02,0:23:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...really nice to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.76,0:23:27.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sanji, Nami, and the others who were \Nbeing chased by Big Mom's ship,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.65,0:23:29.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}have already been on a whole
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:31.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,new adventure on the strangest island ever!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.57,0:23:32.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.55,0:23:34.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,in front of Kid and the others who\Nare aiming to defeat the Four Emperors,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:37.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a pirate who is known as the \Nstrongest among all creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.62,0:23:40.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,on land, sea, and air, descends from the sky!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.82,0:23:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Strongest Creature!\NOne of the Four Emperors - Kaido, King of the Beasts!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ifm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.17,0:23:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
